quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  104,1,"Wɩɩbd be ne wɩt fãa sẽn yaa zangda."
  104,2,"Ned ning sẽn tigim-a a arzεka, n tar a sõdbo."
  104,3,"N sãmbdẽ t'a ligdã na n duums-a lame,"
  104,4,"Pa woto ye! B na n loab-a-la Ḥʋṭama pʋgẽ!"
  104,5,"La bõe n wilgd foo Ḥʋṭama sẽn ya-a soaba?"
  104,6,"Yaa Wẽnd bugum sẽn widgi."
  104,7,"Sẽn rʋʋgd hal sũyẽ."
  104,8,"Yẽnda n na n fõgen-ba."
  104,9,"Tɩ b be zeng-ra-lugds sẽn yɑɑ wogd pʋgẽ."
